headline.print_headline: Coordinated Blasts Target Fatah Officials in Gaza
headline.main: Coordinated Blasts Target Fatah Officials in Gaza

lead_paragraph: A series of coordinated explosions targeted the homes of several leaders of President Mahmoud Abbas' Fatah Party in the Gaza Strip early Friday, a party official said.
